law.text:
A crime stoppers organization shall:
Foster the detection of crime and encourage persons to report information about criminal acts;
Encourage news and other media to promote local crime stoppers organizations and to inform the public of the functions of the organization;
Assist other crime stoppers organizations in forwarding information about criminal acts to the appropriate law enforcement agencies; and
Help law enforcement agencies detect and combat crime by increasing the flow of information to and between law enforcement agencies.
